{
  "stem": "21582.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You know, it was not the material value that, that-- the material loss that really counted that much, except that it's an invasion.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It's just-- it, it, it, it was robbing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was plunder.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I remember as a child asking my mother that I remembered that so often people would say Jews are greedy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And here, the people come into my house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They steal from me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They plunder from me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they call me greedy?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, why did-- why did they take their sons and their husbands and their daughters and send them into war if it was not for greed, if it was not for plunder?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it just absolutely confused me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to surrender things of value-- of value materially, but more above that, of sentimental value.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- I, I don't recall whether the, the water was shut off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I do recall distinctly that it might have been that the pipes were broken.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it seems to me that the water was shut off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember that we had to walk a certain distance with buckets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, [LAUGHS] it was not as though we could go to stores, that the stores were prepared with merchandise that we needed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we had to be very sparing with the water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember we had to go with the buckets for water during the winter where it was slippery and icy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They shut the lights off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we-- and, and, and of course, there were blackouts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we used carbide lights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And books were confiscated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And schools were shut.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
